<h2>Account Deletion Request</h2>
</div>

<div class="policy-card">

<p>
At BH Namoro, we believe you should have full control over your personal data. In strict compliance with Google Play Developer Data Safety Policies, you can request the permanent deletion of your account and all associated data at any time.
</p>

<h3>1. What Information Will Be Deleted?</h3>

<p>When you request to delete your account, the following data is permanently wiped from our systems:</p>

<div class="permissions">
<ul>
<li>Your personal profile information (Name, Gender, Dating Preferences, Bio).</li>
<li>All uploaded photos, images, and media files.</li>
<li>Your entire conversation history and private messages with other users.</li>
<li>Your precise location logs (GPS data) and device identifiers.</li>
<li>Any historical interaction data within the app.</li>
</ul>
</div>

<h3>2. Data Retention and Processing Time</h3>

<p>• <strong>Immediate Effect:</strong> Once you submit your request, your profile is immediately hidden from the discovery pool and becomes completely invisible to other users.</p>

<p>• <strong>Permanent Removal:</strong> All personal data associated with your account will be permanently deleted from our active databases and servers within 48 hours.</p>

<p>• <strong>Legal Exceptions:</strong> We only retain minimum mandatory backup logs if required by specific local laws or to prevent active fraud or harassment investigations.</p>

<h3>3. How to Request Deletion?</h3>

<p>You can request account deletion using either of the following methods:</p>

<div class="permissions">
<p><strong>Method A (In-App):</strong><br>Go to Settings > Account > Delete Account, and confirm your request.</p>

<hr style="margin:15px 0; border:0; border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;">

<p><strong>Method B (Web Request):</strong><br>If you have already uninstalled the app or cannot log in, please send an e-mail directly from your registered email address to: <a href="mailto:support@nyxglobalapps.com">support@nyxglobalapps.com</a><br><strong>Subject:</strong> BH Namoro – Account Deletion Request</p>

<p style="margin-top:5px; font-size:0.95rem; color:var(--text);"><em>Please include your full profile name or username so we can process your request immediately.</em></p>
</div>

